@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_brpoij(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.34 + v2 + 0.91)) - (wp.sin(v1 + 0.67) / (v0 + 0.30 - v0 + 0.62)))
    v1 = (0.99 - v2)
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.63 / v1 + 0.96)) * v1)
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.76)) / (wp.sin(v1 + 0.98) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.88)))
    v2 = (0.12 - wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.99)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.cos(v2 + 0.16) - 0.75))
    data[tid] = v0
